{"tid":1885463,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA20 Ultimate Team 不推文討厭區 (185) 屌你老母1001","createTime":"2020-02-18T10:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T17:27:14.000Z","uid":7232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb203508c5fbeb6deeda48a910c356d074cf398","tid":1885463,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FckjBrs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFckjBrs.gif&h=bb509340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入FIFA20 Ultimate Team討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始前請先睇Q&amp;A，睇完搵唔到你想知嘅野先問，好多你想知嘅野都係第一版！拜託曬！<br />\n<br />\nFIFA UT web app: <a href=\"https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Fweb-app&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=d39c3b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app</a><br />\n<br />\n球員資料database:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://futbin.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffutbin.com&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=d8666654\" target=\"_blank\">http://futbin.com</a><br />\n<br />\nSBC 答案 (參考idea, 抄足貴到仆街)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36xts7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36xts7Q&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=c50ee3d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36xts7Q</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n1.係咪有金包送架?<br />\n答:今年自動送pack，唔使入code<br />\n<br />\n2. 點賺錢?<br />\n答:踏實d, 打比賽, 要快手就去淘寶課金, 但EA話會嚴打買賣coins, 後果自負<br />\n玩耐左可以試下炒卡。<br />\n留意賣卡會收「稅」，成功交易會抽5%，如賣10,000 coins成交，實收9,500<br />\n<br />\n3. 咩係chemistry?<br />\n答:簡單d黎講, 高chemistry d隊員走位好d唔會成碌木咁唔走位, 另外個人chemistry會影響能力<br />\n<br />\n4. 咁點加chemistry呀?<br />\n答:位置、球員之間嘅連線、教練、loyalty等等都會影響chemistry。<br />\n<br />\n5. 咩係綠色連線?<br />\n答:球員同球員之間ge連線:國籍,聯賽,球隊<br />\n符合兩樣就夠有綠色連線<br />\n<br />\n6. 咩係IF?咩係TOTW?點解有d卡會係黑色?<br />\n答:每星期三晚都會有新嘅TOTW (team of the week)<br />\n出嘅人會有張加強版嘅黑色卡，又叫IF (in form)<br />\n<br />\n7.chemistry style係咩黎?持續幾耐?<br />\n答: 唔同chemistry style會對球員某d 能力有唔同提升, 每個球員一開始都有basic呢個style<br />\n你會見到每項能力都有一格V形箭嘴, chemistry style卡係永遠套用於某個球員, 直至你apply另一張落去<br />\n<br />\n8: 你地成日講H/H, H/M, M/L 係乜勁呀?<br />\n答: 代表球員work rate, H-high, M-medium, L-low<br />\n<br />\n9: 乜野係ONE TO WATCH呢？<br />\n答: 就係呢個球員今季先轉會，咁就有幸比FIFA觀察<br />\notw卡 係會跟inform卡 upgrade數值，卡面都會跟埋IF<br />\n<br />\n10:我DR SB 幾分幾分夠唔夠KEEP RANK 1?<br />\n答:<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2oMWQ9m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oMWQ9m&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=c0d5760f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2oMWQ9m</a><br />\n<br />\n11:點樣開新po？<br />\n答: 去#1右上角三點，禁以此內容開新主題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMetqpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMetqpP.png&h=603a033d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12:頭5場WL 有咩用? 究竟WL 係點配對手俾我? <br />\n頭5場對手係random但決定你的起手ranking<br />\n贏曬即係+5 赢3場即係+1+1+1-1-1 &gt; +1 已經有極大既分別<br />\n<br />\n13: 對手球會/陣容名損害我哋七百萬人嘅心靈，可以點做？<br />\n答: 唔檢舉唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Nb400w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Nb400w&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=be3c5407\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Nb400w</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g00mYmG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg00mYmG.png&h=825699be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14:咩叫肥料卡，META卡？<br />\n答:肥料就係作用解SBC、靚國藉靚聯賽、高rate低能嘅人。META=實用球員，唔受總分所限 , 玩家覺得勁嘅卡<br />\n<br />\n15:藍卡，RTTF又係啲乜？<br />\n答: 藍卡 = UCL 卡 , 有得打歐冠先有嘅卡/RTTF = ROAD TO THE FINAL, 踢緊歐聯嘅球員 , 佢每晉一級就會升一分總分<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/3735GB0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3735GB0&h=ed0af756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16:點解我交唔到SBC/做唔到OBJ？<br />\n答: 開機交/睇英文版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVA9s5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVA9s5U.png&h=c48531bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBppBac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBppBac.gif&h=dfaa4189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我愛EA！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ7nFg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ7nFg0.jpg&h=5df15dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nICON SWAPS 2<br />\n由即日起至二月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dahV7HV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdahV7HV.jpg&h=d1d378bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkG6g43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkG6g43.jpg&h=071b10d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wow9YYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwow9YYC.jpg&h=cc882075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLPvJpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLPvJpH.jpg&h=e37eba0e&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"377c04f56ada0f80b4bce680365224e6d54b598b","tid":1885463,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1001開po呀屌你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dc4cf7144ac105dd50723c7fd9ed15ba8dc78c55","tid":1885463,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"屌，同時開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fee21713a950fd4628c64d02d158ebb4de75553","tid":1885463,"uid":324556,"like":0,"dislik